table_caption: ANOVA effect of sex and TIV (estimate (standard error) and significance p value) on five DTI metrics (AD, RD, MD, PSMD, and FA evaluated across individual FA skeletons).
table_foot: Values for the effects of sex are in mm2 s−1 × 10−6 for AD, RD, MD, and PSMD and in ×10−3 for FA, and for the effects of TIV are in mm2 s−1 cm−3 × 10−6 for AD, RD MD, and PSMD and in cm−3 × 10−5 for FA.
